Merge pull request #9 from last-g/patch-1

Remove setup dependency on flake8

Remove setup dependency on flake8 

* flake8 is not (and should not be) install dependency of this package
* flake8 is now kinda crapy because depends on flakes<1.1, but modern installations of  python contain preinstalled flakes 1.1. So installation of stups-tokens fails
require a more recent requests version supporting timeout tuples (connect, read)
#6 set proper User-Agent header
#5 add connect and socket timeouts (1.25s/2.25s slightly higher than Java tokens lib)

Merge pull request #4 from zalando-stups/add-ignore-expire-feature

Added ignore_expire in manage() to continue using expired tokens in error cases
we need to throw an exception if we never got any access token
rename to "ignore_expiration"
Flake error fixed
Added ignore_expire in manage() to continue using expired tokens in error cases. Added expires_at to other unit test, believe otherwise it is key error exception and not request exception
